key: content description
content-length: 694

John Hardy, renowned for his artisan-crafted luxury jewellery, has been based in Bali since 1975. Thoughtfully hand-crafted jewellery built on a tradition of artistry that dates back to the ancient Balinese courts, every John Hardy piece is powerful, dramatic and inspiring.  As an artist visiting Bali in the 1970s Hardy was enraptured by the vitality of island life, its rich culture and simple and pure lifestyle. There, he discovered the inspiring tradition of artistry among the Balinese, especially their skill for hand-crafting jewellery. He settled in Bali and built a brand that 40 years later, still embodies the ultimate beauty of jewellery that is powerful, dramatic and inspiring. 
